Kam, take a look at the hostage.

19
00:03:26,706 --> 00:03:28,503
You bastards, shooting at the hostage!

20
00:03:28,641 --> 00:03:30,131
I'll sue you.

21
00:03:30,276 --> 00:03:31,573
