I told him the gun misfired.

24
00:03:37,317 --> 00:03:38,511
He says he'll sue.

25
00:03:38,952 --> 00:03:41,250
These guns are supplied by the U.K.

26
00:03:41,387 --> 00:03:43,184
Go sue the England.

27
00:03:43,289 --> 00:03:44,688
- And he started crying.
- Kam.

28
00:03:44,824 --> 00:03:46,121
You go ahead first.

29
00:03:46,826 --> 00:03:49,818
The boss wants to see us.
Let's take his lecture together.

30
00:03:53,633 --> 00:03:55,225
What a mess!

31
