536
00:49:59,830 --> 00:50:00,524
Shit!

537
00:50:06,303 --> 00:50:08,498
That guy's hanging.

538
00:50:17,581 --> 00:50:20,379
Help me! I can't take it, save me!

539
00:50:27,657 --> 00:50:28,851
I can see him, John!

540
00:50:29,259 --> 00:50:30,351
Is he near to you now?

541
00:50:30,494 --> 00:50:31,893
Yes, I'll get him.

542
00:50:32,629 --> 00:50:33,527
Help!

543
00:50:43,206 --> 00:50:45,401
It's dangerous, he's got a grenade.

544
00:50:47,744 --> 00:50:52,841
Help!

545
00:51:00,290 --> 00:51:01,689
Oh Shit!

546
00:51:26,016 --> 00:51:27,415
Get Doctor Chang!

547
00:51:29,152 --> 00:51:31,347
Mind the way, excuse me!

548
00:51:32,756 --> 00:51:35,554
Oxygen, we need oxygen.

549
00:51:37,094 --> 00:51:37,890
Let's help him, alright?

550
00:51:38,028 --> 00:51:39,222
Hurry, why blood won't come?

551
00:51:42,899 --> 00:51:46,596
- Excuse me!
- Blood... hurry up!

552
00:51:48,071 --> 00:51:49,265
Come here, help me, hurry up!

553
00:51:50,640 --> 00:51:51,834
Hold the salt water bottle, hurry up!

554
00:52:46,596 --> 00:52:48,393
We've got Ho's statement.

555
00:52:48,498 --> 00:52:49,795
Why can't we go and get Han now?

556
00:52:52,869 --> 00:52:54,359
Ho is dead.

557
00:52:54,504 --> 00:52:56,096
You go and alert Han now,

558
00:52:56,139 --> 00:52:58,334
he'll sue you like hell, idiot!

559
00:52:58,942 --> 00:53:02,935
That's true. Last year a guy
cheated so much money from the banks,

560
00:53:03,079 --> 00:53:04,774
but he was judged not guilty.

561
00:53:05,048 --> 00:53:06,345
It's a mess anyway.

562
00:53:19,462 --> 00:53:22,056
What is it? All your fathers died?

563
00:53:24,134 --> 00:53:25,431
This case is not over yet.

564
00:53:27,337 --> 00:53:28,634
Look at this.

565
00:53:31,641 --> 00:53:32,539
Powdered milk.

566
00:53:33,343 --> 00:53:35,937
That's right, what's wrong?

567
00:53:36,246 --> 00:53:38,339
If so many
can get killed over powdered milk,

568
00:53:39,049 --> 00:53:40,346
women wouldn't dare have children.

569
00:53:41,218 --> 00:53:42,515
Let's take it for tests.

570
00:54:01,137 --> 00:54:03,298
We have an informer in the police.

571
00:54:03,373 --> 00:54:07,002
You must help us find out
what this stuff is.

572
00:54:19,990 --> 00:54:22,390
What are these? Plant seeds.

573
00:54:31,067 --> 00:54:34,468
I'll let you know.

574
00:54:36,439 --> 00:54:38,634
It's urgent but you be careful.

575
00:54:39,042 --> 00:54:41,442
Nobody must know about it.

576
00:54:42,746 --> 00:54:44,941
I'll conduct the tests
when none is around.

577
00:54:54,224 --> 00:54:55,714
Call me when you have the results.

578
00:54:56,493 --> 00:54:58,586
I'll wait for your call.

579
00:55:00,130 --> 00:55:01,119
John.

580
00:55:03,400 --> 00:55:05,459
Let's go. It's a family affair.

581
00:55:05,702 --> 00:55:06,600
Wait!

582
00:55:13,076 --> 00:55:15,010
This is your birthday gift to me.

583
00:55:16,346 --> 00:55:17,313
Do you want it back?

584
00:55:59,189 --> 00:56:01,384
I'll call you with the results.

585
00:56:01,691 --> 00:56:02,988
Just take care.

586
00:56:05,562 --> 00:56:06,654
I will.

587
00:56:08,064 --> 00:56:09,759
I hope I can help you break the case.

588
00:56:24,214 --> 00:56:26,114
He's back, quiet.

589
00:56:27,717 --> 00:56:30,015
These guys have really got guts.

590
00:56:31,221 --> 00:56:32,620
Following us again!

591
00:56:35,558 --> 00:56:38,049
What do we do?

592
00:56:38,261 --> 00:56:40,957
Calm down, they won't get away.

593
00:56:42,465 --> 00:56:44,160
Hawk calling H.Q., I'm P.C. Chan.

594
00:56:44,267 --> 00:56:46,258
According to the information,
we discovered the drug dealer.

595
00:56:46,369 --> 00:56:48,064
We must stick an eye on him, over.

596
00:56:59,082 --> 00:57:01,073
This is Inspector Wong.

597
00:57:01,251 --> 00:57:02,741
I'm going past Sheung Wan Street.

598
00:57:02,886 --> 00:57:05,354
One light brown 4-door sedan,

599
00:57:05,455 --> 00:57:07,855
registration B.T. 6041.

600
00:57:07,991 --> 00:57:09,982
4 suspects in the car.

601
00:57:10,160 --> 00:57:12,560
We are proceeding to Wing Lok Street.

602
00:57:12,729 --> 00:57:14,663
Keep an eye on them, over!

603
00:57:23,840 --> 00:57:24,932
We've got to catch them today.

604
00:57:25,108 --> 00:57:26,097
Here they come.

605
00:57:47,030 --> 00:57:48,429
I've never had a gun fight yet.

606
00:57:48,531 --> 00:57:49,520
Shut the door and watch the fun.

607
00:57:59,008 --> 00:58:00,805
Looks like they're armed.

608
00:58:14,557 --> 00:58:15,581
They're armed.

609
00:58:15,725 --> 00:58:17,420
Get some help.

610
00:58:18,161 --> 00:58:20,061
Those inside do not move. We are C.I.D.

611
00:58:22,031 --> 00:58:24,329
We're C.I.D. Too.
Why are you following us?

612
00:58:24,634 --> 00:58:26,727
We'll shoot if you don't come out.

613
00:58:27,203 --> 00:58:30,695
Shit, whoever shoots first gets it.

614
00:58:35,278 --> 00:58:36,575
Get down!

615
00:58:41,050 --> 00:58:42,347
Put your I.D. Away.

616
00:58:42,952 --> 00:58:43,850
They are getting out their guns.

617
00:58:51,194 --> 00:58:54,595
Kam, Ong, don't shoot.
Someone is playing a bad joke on us.

618
00:58:54,731 --> 00:58:56,130
Kam, Ong!

619
00:58:59,435 --> 00:59:00,527
Really C.I.D.'s.

620
00:59:04,841 --> 00:59:05,933
How are you?

621
00:59:33,803 --> 00:59:35,998
- A gun fight!
- This serious?

622
00:59:36,706 --> 00:59:38,105
Someone was lying in wait for us.

623
00:59:38,274 --> 00:59:40,572
- Attack the police? Seal the place!
- Yes, sir!

624
00:59:40,677 --> 00:59:42,577
Looks like guys from the next district.

625
00:59:42,779 --> 00:59:45,873
Bad luck for them,
barging in on us like this.

626
00:59:55,258 --> 00:59:56,748
You jerks come up with something new
each day.

627
00:59:56,893 --> 00:59:58,588
Don't let news of this get out.

628
00:59:58,728 --> 01:00:01,526
Or it will make the top 10 charts.

629
01:00:01,631 --> 01:00:04,896
Our crime unit says
someone is following them,

630
01:00:06,135 --> 01:00:09,662
someone gave us a tip-off
to follow your guys, Sir!

631
01:00:10,707 --> 01:00:13,107
- Tell them all to come out. Now.
- Yes, Sir!

632
01:00:13,409 --> 01:00:15,502
All of you inside come out.

633
01:00:16,479 --> 01:00:18,970
This is Ng. Don't come out.

634
01:00:23,920 --> 01:00:26,411
How can you guarantee your guys
won't attack my guys.

635
01:00:26,623 --> 01:00:29,114
If my guys were to shoot,
your guys can't come out.

636
01:00:29,292 --> 01:00:30,884
I guarantee their safety.

637
01:00:31,294 --> 01:00:32,488
O.K.

638
01:00:33,196 --> 01:00:34,993
I'm Law from Central.

639
01:00:35,198 --> 01:00:36,790
Our guys come out.

640
01:01:00,256 --> 01:01:02,554
Who started the shooting?

641
01:01:02,725 --> 01:01:04,784
I'll put this in my report,
you just wait.

642
01:01:08,598 --> 01:01:09,895
I fired the first shot.

643
01:01:11,234 --> 01:01:14,465
People like you ruin the police's image.

644
01:01:23,413 --> 01:01:26,246
Do you think that Peter arranged this.

645
01:01:37,126 --> 01:01:38,423
Isn't that Ching Han?

646
01:01:48,104 --> 01:01:49,799
Inspector Wong, pleased to meet you.

647
01:01:54,544 --> 01:01:55,636
How are you?

648
01:01:56,179 --> 01:01:58,272
I hear your gang is very thorough, good!

649
01:02:04,253 --> 01:02:08,246
Hong Kong has only 10 years left,
not much time.

650
01:02:08,858 --> 01:02:10,655
How can we make a living
if we are not thorough.

651
01:02:11,661 --> 01:02:12,855
You know we are investigating you.

652
01:02:12,962 --> 01:02:15,396
You have your hands on my shoulders,
wanna deal?

653
01:02:17,633 --> 01:02:20,329
I don't know about deals.

654
01:02:21,904 --> 01:02:23,496
I knew you'd come looking for me.

655
01:02:24,173 --> 01:02:25,868
That's why I've come voluntarily.

656
01:02:26,209 --> 01:02:28,404
Go ahead, ask.
I'll try my best to answer.

657
01:02:28,911 --> 01:02:32,403
The answers you can give
are probably not good enough.

658
01:02:34,751 --> 01:02:36,742
No hurry, I'll be looking for you.

659
01:02:37,186 --> 01:02:40,849
Don't get a ticket for Seattle
when the time comes.

660
01:02:40,890 --> 01:02:43,085
You dropped something.

661
01:02:43,426 --> 01:02:44,825
Take it home and look it over.

662
01:03:02,712 --> 01:03:05,681
I don't know which beggar
threw that dirty money away.

663
01:03:13,122 --> 01:03:14,521
Tell him to go eat shit.

664
01:03:56,899 --> 01:03:58,196
Did you see that face!

665
01:03:58,401 --> 01:04:00,699
Watching us throw his money away.

666
01:04:00,803 --> 01:04:02,600
- What fun!
- Fun, eh!

667
01:04:02,672 --> 01:04:05,539
My heart broke when I saw that money go.

668
01:04:25,428 --> 01:04:28,022
You can't suspend me now.

669
01:04:28,130 --> 01:04:29,722
I'm nearly there.

670
01:04:29,899 --> 01:04:31,196
Let me go on.

671
01:04:31,334 --> 01:04:33,529
How can there be
suddenly $300,000 in my bank?

672
01:04:33,636 --> 01:04:35,126
Someone is setting me up.

673
01:04:36,205 --> 01:04:38,105
Sorry, I.C.A.C. Is after you.

674
01:04:38,441 --> 01:04:40,238
Even then, I don't need to be suspended.

675
01:04:40,276 --> 01:04:42,574
When will we get enough evidence
to get Han?

676
01:04:42,712 --> 01:04:44,805
You talk to the I.C.A.C.

677
01:04:45,047 --> 01:04:47,447
Just give me one more month.

678
01:04:47,583 --> 01:04:49,278
Otherwise
all my work goes down the drain.

679
01:04:49,452 --> 01:04:50,111
Superintendent, Wong...

680
01:04:50,152 --> 01:04:51,346
Anymore from you,
you get an investigation too.

681
01:04:52,455 --> 01:04:55,049
Lun, don't mess about. I'll fix the boss.

682
01:05:00,029 --> 01:05:01,929
Ho was murdered at the hospital.

683
01:05:02,832 --> 01:05:03,821
This case is not finished yet.

684
01:05:03,966 --> 01:05:06,730
You'll be busy at the Courts
all the time.

685
01:05:14,443 --> 01:05:15,774
Don't go on investigating this month.

686
01:05:15,912 --> 01:05:17,402
I've got to make a call.

687
01:05:20,049 --> 01:05:21,846
Lun, Maggie called.

688
01:05:21,951 --> 01:05:23,248
- Go and see what it is.
- OK.

689
01:05:35,264 --> 01:05:37,164
Hello, Maggie, Lun here.

690
01:05:37,466 --> 01:05:40,629
I've got it, it's cocaine seeds.

691
01:05:40,736 --> 01:05:42,431
After refinement, it becomes heroin.

692
01:05:42,571 --> 01:05:44,869
I'll tell Inspector Wong!

693
01:07:33,282 --> 01:07:34,476
One and half minutes left.

694
01:07:35,117 --> 01:07:36,015
Throw it out the window.

695
01:07:38,721 --> 01:07:40,211
No, there are pedestrians.

696
01:07:40,923 --> 01:07:42,322
- There's building site there.
- Excuse me!

697
01:07:43,659 --> 01:07:46,150
- Move over!
- Excuse...

698
01:07:46,962 --> 01:07:48,156
This way! Hurry up!

699
01:07:51,634 --> 01:07:52,623
Excuse...

700
01:07:53,836 --> 01:07:56,737
- That's way! Hurry up!
- What do you do?

701
01:08:00,509 --> 01:08:01,908
Calling H. Q!

702
01:08:03,012 --> 01:08:04,001
Move off!

703
01:08:04,780 --> 01:08:05,974
I'll shoot if you don't stop.

704
01:08:06,615 --> 01:08:07,604
What is it?

705
01:08:09,552 --> 01:08:10,450
Hurry up!

706
01:08:11,854 --> 01:08:13,151
I'm C.I. D!

707
01:08:20,596 --> 01:08:21,585
Move off!

708
01:08:23,732 --> 01:08:26,223
Don't run... l'll shoot.

709
01:08:45,154 --> 01:08:46,451
You're idiot!

710
01:08:48,624 --> 01:08:49,682
Are you O.K. Kam?

711
01:08:50,226 --> 01:08:54,322
You're right, I'm slow.

712
01:08:54,463 --> 01:08:57,364
To let that old soldier shoot me,
shit on shit.

713
01:08:58,100 --> 01:08:59,089
You...

714
01:09:00,469 --> 01:09:02,061
My mother is really stubborn.

715
01:09:02,171 --> 01:09:03,866
She mustn't know I'm shot.

716
01:09:12,748 --> 01:09:15,581
Kam...

717
01:09:19,488 --> 01:09:23,083
Do you know where my son Kam is?

718
01:09:23,292 --> 01:09:25,692
The cop with the bad temper?

719
01:09:25,794 --> 01:09:27,284
Right, where is he?

720
01:09:27,496 --> 01:09:31,694
- In bed number 52.
- Thank you! Kam!

721
01:09:33,235 --> 01:09:34,429
Oh Shit!

722
01:10:02,831 --> 01:10:05,129
- Who shall I say it's from?
- Waipong Wong?

723
01:10:05,401 --> 01:10:08,097
- How much?
- Waipong Wong, $200.

724
01:10:55,417 --> 01:10:58,614
Attention! Start!

725
01:11:15,170 --> 01:11:18,435
John! You have to go to Court tomorrow.

726
01:11:24,980 --> 01:11:26,675
I'm going back to K.L. Tomorrow.

727
01:11:27,182 --> 01:11:29,275
Your boss reported on me to my boss.

728
01:11:30,085 --> 01:11:32,076
H.Q. Wants me back.

729
01:11:34,757 --> 01:11:37,248
Can't send you off.

730
01:11:38,060 --> 01:11:39,550
- Take care!
- I will!

731
01:11:42,264 --> 01:11:43,663
Sorry! Wong!

732
01:11:43,866 --> 01:11:46,562
I don't know
whether it's the right time to resign.

733
01:11:47,002 --> 01:11:49,402
My mother is afraid I'll get killed.

734
01:11:51,373 --> 01:11:53,068
She needs me to take care of her.

735
01:11:57,112 --> 01:11:59,307
Don't worry, I'll fix it.

736
01:12:00,683 --> 01:12:02,674
If you need help, anytime.

737
01:12:05,154 --> 01:12:08,146
"The Supreme Court"

738
01:12:08,457 --> 01:12:11,358
Do you have any comments
on this investigation?

739
01:12:11,560 --> 01:12:12,652
Sorry, no comments.

740
01:12:12,995 --> 01:12:14,087
Mr. Han!

741
01:12:14,430 --> 01:12:16,057
How come you're involved in this?

742
01:12:16,131 --> 01:12:17,325
Actually decent businessmen like me,

743
01:12:17,466 --> 01:12:19,866
hate law keepers who are corrupt. Sorry!

744
01:12:21,470 --> 01:12:23,461
I never knew
we'd see one another in Court.

745
01:12:24,206 --> 01:12:26,504
But you're not after me, I'm after you.

746
01:12:27,476 --> 01:12:31,173
Frankly,
this is your chance to go straight.

747
01:12:31,513 --> 01:12:33,003
I feel sorry for you too.

748
01:12:34,717 --> 01:12:37,117
I've always doubted Hong Kong's law,

749
01:12:37,586 --> 01:12:39,781
but a lot of people
are wasting good time,

750
01:12:39,988 --> 01:12:42,479
nowadays studying basic law,
actually there is no law.

751
01:12:43,092 --> 01:12:44,286
Small matter.

752
01:12:44,493 --> 01:12:47,587
Spend a few years inside. Start again.

753
01:12:47,930 --> 01:12:49,329
Don't worry. Nothing will happen.

754
01:12:49,665 --> 01:12:51,860
Any problems, call me.

755
01:13:07,416 --> 01:13:08,610
You bastard.

756
01:13:24,199 --> 01:13:29,102
- Don't fight!
- Let him go!

757
01:13:30,005 --> 01:13:31,404
- Bastard!
- Don't fight!

758
01:13:32,241 --> 01:13:34,038
Excuse me! Don't fight!

759
01:13:35,444 --> 01:13:39,039
Let me go, I'll beat him to death.

760
01:13:42,651 --> 01:13:44,642
Don't bother, kid.
You need some vitamin pills.

761
01:13:46,455 --> 01:13:47,353
Let's go!

762
01:13:49,291 --> 01:13:50,690
Don't you leave.

763
01:13:50,859 --> 01:13:52,759
- There are reporters here.
- Let me go!

764
01:13:52,961 --> 01:13:56,863
- Don't fail for it!
- I can't live with it.

765
01:13:58,333 --> 01:14:00,028
If this is what a cop's life is, I quit.

766
01:14:00,636 --> 01:14:03,537
- Lun!
- Lun. Kwok Keung Lun!

767
01:14:05,741 --> 01:14:07,732
Lun. Kwok Keung Lun!

768
01:14:11,313 --> 01:14:13,110
- Where are you off to?
- Come on!

769
01:14:15,651 --> 01:14:19,246
Lun...

770
01:14:36,572 --> 01:14:37,470
$15!

771
01:14:41,910 --> 01:14:45,004
That's right. Just let it blow over.

772
01:14:45,214 --> 01:14:46,408
Love forever!

773
01:14:53,455 --> 01:14:56,856
- $58.
- Miss! Give me a lighter.

774
01:14:57,292 --> 01:14:58,486
- O. K!
- $15.

775
01:15:08,203 --> 01:15:09,295
What is it?

776
01:15:09,505 --> 01:15:11,097
Notify Inspector Wong and Kam.

777
01:15:11,240 --> 01:15:13,435
Tell them to wait, I've got a new clue.

778
01:15:41,803 --> 01:15:42,701
Let's go!

779
01:15:43,105 --> 01:15:45,005
At least you have to tell me where to go.

780
01:15:45,173 --> 01:15:46,572
I'm C.I.D. Follow that Rolls Royce.

781
01:15:47,009 --> 01:15:48,101
After some robbers?

782
01:15:56,952 --> 01:15:58,249
Where did you go?

783
01:15:58,320 --> 01:15:59,218
Don't ask me to do dangerous things.

784
01:15:59,354 --> 01:16:01,549
You take the car,
I'll get it back from police station.

785
01:16:42,998 --> 01:16:46,365
You bungled the job,
the cargo nearly didn't go out.

786
01:16:46,535 --> 01:16:47,934
It will be even more inconvenient.

787
01:16:48,003 --> 01:16:49,300
The police are watching us.

788
01:16:49,972 --> 01:16:52,463
Our transport network in S.E. Asia,

789
01:16:52,641 --> 01:16:54,734
has been completely destroyed by you.

790
01:16:55,911 --> 01:16:57,606
Ching Han, you are a man of resources,

791
01:16:57,746 --> 01:16:59,737
now there's a problem, what then?

792
01:17:00,048 --> 01:17:03,449
Mr. Molotov,
Hong Kong will be handed over soon,

793
01:17:04,853 --> 01:17:06,946
many are waiting to emigrate.

794
01:17:07,489 --> 01:17:08,387
They need money.

795
01:17:08,557 --> 01:17:09,956
I agree with you.

796
01:17:10,125 --> 01:17:12,320
This is the time to grab money.

797
01:17:12,494 --> 01:17:13,791
As long as we pay the price,

798
01:17:13,962 --> 01:17:15,156
not to mention drugs,

799
01:17:15,297 --> 01:17:17,322
you can ship
the entire Hong Kong to your country.

800
01:17:17,532 --> 01:17:20,433
This list are high government officials.

801
01:17:20,535 --> 01:17:21,832
Yes, we spent some money,

802
01:17:21,937 --> 01:17:23,427
but compared to our profits,

803
01:17:23,605 --> 01:17:27,006
this investment is peanuts.

804
01:17:30,612 --> 01:17:33,206
Traveler Chat Fu Ong,
who took flight 071 to Malaysia,

805
01:17:33,382 --> 01:17:37,079
please contact
the airport enquiry center.

806
01:17:39,087 --> 01:17:43,080
You're right.
Everybody looks to money now.

807
01:17:43,291 --> 01:17:47,887
Selling drugs and capitalism together
is the best way.

808
01:17:48,530 --> 01:17:51,226
Let's drink to 1997.

809
01:17:51,333 --> 01:17:53,733
- Cheers!
- To greater success.

810
01:18:10,819 --> 01:18:12,514
Mr. Han,
that rookie has followed us here.

811
01:19:01,536 --> 01:19:02,434
Freeze!

812
01:19:03,672 --> 01:19:05,640
Trying to scare somebody?

813
01:19:06,842 --> 01:19:08,742
- Have you called Inspector Wong!
- He'll be here soon.

814
01:19:09,644 --> 01:19:11,942
I've recorded Han's meeting.

815
01:19:12,080 --> 01:19:14,071
He's moving drugs for the Russians.

816
01:19:14,249 --> 01:19:15,841
Han's nailed this time.

817
01:19:19,888 --> 01:19:20,980
Lun!

818
01:19:23,191 --> 01:19:24,283
It's that guy.

819
01:19:35,937 --> 01:19:37,336
Can't call out.

820
01:19:42,878 --> 01:19:44,277
Go through that window.

821
01:19:47,015 --> 01:19:48,312
Jump down, quick.

822
01:19:52,888 --> 01:19:54,185
And give the tape to Inspector Wong!

823
01:21:02,991 --> 01:21:06,256
How come your face can be cut by a blade?

824
01:21:06,695 --> 01:21:08,595
I thought it was made of steel.

825
01:21:09,030 --> 01:21:11,021
I despise stupid people like you.

826
01:21:11,132 --> 01:21:12,724
You do not treasure your life.

827
01:21:14,269 --> 01:21:16,066
You go all the way each time,

828
01:21:16,605 --> 01:21:19,403
with no ulterior motive, no gains.

829
01:21:19,841 --> 01:21:21,536
I don't know for what.

830
01:21:22,410 --> 01:21:26,540
I thought stubborn people like you
have already become extinct.

831
01:21:29,618 --> 01:21:31,518
Mr. Han, we found the tape.

832
01:21:31,720 --> 01:21:32,618
Other than the kid,

833
01:21:32,721 --> 01:21:35,121
others must know our secret too.

834
01:21:40,195 --> 01:21:43,687
Pity, bad enough for you.

835
01:21:45,133 --> 01:21:48,125
Why did you get others involved?

836
01:21:48,870 --> 01:21:54,775
You want a quick death,
tell me who's heard this tape before.

837
01:22:08,890 --> 01:22:10,084
The janitor is dead.

838
01:22:58,907 --> 01:22:59,896
Lun!

839
01:23:00,208 --> 01:23:01,607
Don't, Lun!

840
01:23:01,743 --> 01:23:05,144
- Let me go!
- Don't go over there.

841
01:23:05,513 --> 01:23:08,414
- Lun...
- Sir.

842
01:23:18,460 --> 01:23:20,257
Lun!

843
01:23:21,930 --> 01:23:25,627
Lun!

844
01:23:36,344 --> 01:23:37,140
Let's go!

845
01:24:20,422 --> 01:24:21,320
Hide.

846
01:24:30,465 --> 01:24:31,454
Cari mati!

847
01:24:37,872 --> 01:24:38,668
Let's go!

848
01:24:41,876 --> 01:24:42,865
That's way!

849
01:24:44,045 --> 01:24:47,139
Kam...

850
01:26:56,444 --> 01:26:57,536
Hurry!

851
01:27:31,479 --> 01:27:32,776
I'll smash you to death.

852
01:27:54,168 --> 01:27:55,260
Don't release the pedal.

853
01:28:04,112 --> 01:28:05,306
Jump, we're crashing.

854
01:28:29,103 --> 01:28:31,196
- Are you O. K?
- No problem!

855
01:29:21,489 --> 01:29:23,980
You bastard, go to hell!

856
01:29:43,211 --> 01:29:44,906
Few years later will be 1997.

857
01:29:45,012 --> 01:29:47,412
Many people are waiting for immigration.

858
01:29:47,582 --> 01:29:48,674
They need money.

859
01:29:48,816 --> 01:29:50,215
I agree with you.

860
01:29:50,385 --> 01:29:52,580
We should take this time
and earn some money.

861
01:29:52,720 --> 01:29:54,517
As long as we can pay for it,

862
01:29:54,689 --> 01:29:55,883
not only smuggling drug,

863
01:29:55,957 --> 01:29:58,255
I can smuggle everything in Hong Kong
to your place.

864
01:29:58,393 --> 01:30:01,487
People in the list
are important people in the government.

865
01:30:31,292 --> 01:30:33,487
We never found out who's on Han's list.

866
01:30:33,628 --> 01:30:36,119
But the drugs leaving Hong Kong
were found by the Marine Police.

867
01:30:36,297 --> 01:30:38,492
At least your efforts were not wasted.

868
01:30:48,676 --> 01:30:51,167
The doctor says my stitches
will be removed next month.

869
01:30:51,379 --> 01:30:52,869
I want to apply to be with you.

870
01:30:53,080 --> 01:30:54,479
I thought you wanted to quit.

871
01:30:54,649 --> 01:30:55,547
On second thoughts,

872
01:30:55,683 --> 01:30:58,481
in this world,
it would be safer to carry a gun.

873
01:31:09,797 --> 01:31:12,789
Excuse me, which one is Inspector Wong?

874
01:31:13,000 --> 01:31:14,797
I've been transferred from
the Western District.

875
01:31:14,969 --> 01:31:16,994
Number 1003, Chuchia Butt!

876
01:31:17,238 --> 01:31:19,433
Don't know where he's...

877
01:31:19,607 --> 01:31:20,301
I am Waipong Wong!

878
01:31:20,441 --> 01:31:21,931
We'll talk about it back in the station.

879
01:31:22,109 --> 01:31:22,905
Yes, Sir!

880
01:31:25,580 --> 01:31:27,980
This car, don't you want your own car?

881
01:31:28,182 --> 01:31:29,080
No, sir!

882
01:31:29,717 --> 01:31:32,015
Working with this long-haired weirdo,
shit!

883
01:31:37,625 --> 01:31:39,616
Wait me!

